---

Tasks:
(1)
Document Owner ( a user ):
- Document upload
- Document parsing
- Document split and view
- Submit -> Sentences with sequences

(2)
Given a sentence id in an yet-to-be translated article
- Display the requested line and the corresponding original language
- Display previous and next lines with help of current line
- Display

(3)
- Setup Google Transliterate for languages present
http://code.google.com/apis/language/transliterate/v1/customtransliteration.html
http://code.google.com/apis/language/transliterate/v1/getting_started.html
http://code.google.com/apis/language/transliterate/v1/reference.html

See keyboard layouts
http://code.google.com/apis/language/virtualkeyboard/v1/kbd_keyboard.html?name=te_phone ( There are also transformation rules )

Indian Languages that Google does not support -
Assamese, Bodo, Dogri, Kashmiri, Konkani, Maithili, Manipuri, Santhali, Sindhi


